{"tid":1424323,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"村上春樹: 我永不割蓆,不篤灰 (無論雞蛋多麼錯，我永遠站在雞蛋那邊)","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T14:07:51.000Z","uid":76078,"like":112,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"409236576fd19f7b645e96471a97a45846140909","tid":1424323,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:41:02.000Z","msg":"村上春樹: <br />\n在高大堅硬的牆和雞蛋之間，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無論高牆是多麼正確，雞蛋是多麼錯誤</span></span></strong>，我永遠站在雞蛋那邊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成日講<span style=\"color: red;\">高牆</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">雞蛋</span>,<br />\n兩面未相搏時梗係支持雞蛋啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>但村上春樹其實係講緊, 就算雞蛋點錯, 都支持雞蛋</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3f37246dea2f967e9ccf1dc7ca142048f7a08f0e","tid":1424323,"uid":76078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd195d7df99a6943fba0869b6fb117d35644ff99","tid":1424323,"uid":76078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:29:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa62c37163b8e958b9ad76fd5d6fffc34d412ebc","tid":1424323,"uid":76078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:11:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74574668409f0ee348ad2f0ba05d6832a2fd9137","tid":1424323,"uid":76078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:44:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c86104886e18e82f172e602a80f24430ce3a3134","tid":1424323,"uid":281584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"28b25d073f4d25350934ab27aa6b23bb1c3a5b1a","tid":1424323,"uid":76078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:24:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f3c673be66092d75d9a381f078728a81fb5c20c8","tid":1424323,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:07:25.000Z","msg":"push"}